{{What were the challenges:}}
Before starting to work on ShopiCSV I hadn't worked a so much with JavaScript and {{React}}, same goes with Auth0, {{AWS}}, internationalization and proper {{CI/CD}}.
Thankfully, I was able to use my {{extensive experience}} with software engineering and {{project management}} to bring this project to a point where I could {{demo it}} to get my next job as a software engineer while awaiting for my son's birth.
